UID:stream-22642211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260217T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T211200Z
DTSTART:20260310T213000Z
DTEND:20260310T233000Z
SUMMARY:Euro Truck Simulator 2 | Ep. 7 - I Meant to Take That Exit
DESCRIPTION:Back behind the wheel in Euro Truck Simulator 2 for more
 long-haul deliveries across Europe. Smooth driving, scenic highways... and
 the occasional \"that wasn't the right turn.\" Travel across Europe as
 king of the road, a trucker who delivers important cargo across impressive
 distances! With dozens of cities to explore, your endurance, skill and
 speed will all be pushed to their limits.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1_kr-6HalaU
CATEGORIES:Euro Truck Simulator 2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22652211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260218T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T211200Z
DTSTART:20260311T213000Z
DTEND:20260311T233000Z
SUMMARY:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered | Ep. 4 - Opernplatz
DESCRIPTION:The stealth continues in Sniper Elite V2 Remastered. Careful
 positioning, patience, and those signature slow-motion moments. In the
 dark days of the end of World War 2 amidst the ruins of Berlin, one bullet
 can change history... Elite sniper Karl Fairburne returns to the front
 line in the remaster of this award-winning stealth-action experience.
 Packed with new features, contemporary visuals and definitive content.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v5daWIt_Gc8
CATEGORIES:Sniper Elite V2 Remastered
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:stream-22662211@dr-ravenholm
DTSTAMP:20260219T010000Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260313T211200Z
DTSTART:20260312T213000Z
DTEND:20260312T233000Z
SUMMARY:Before We Leave | Ep. 1 - The Peeps Have Discovered Potatoes.
 Civilization Begins
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new series begins in Before We Leave. Our little
 colony of Peeps is stepping out into the world, discovering resources, and
 apparently building civilization on potatoes. Before We Leave is a city
 building game set in a cozy corner of the universe. Nurture your Peeps and
 their surroundings while rebuilding and rediscovering civilisation. Settle
 new lands and planets while avoiding hungry Space Whales.
URL:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K4VFLmsC7aQ
CATEGORIES:Before We Leave
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
